:

1. *Ona je bila zaljubljena u njega.* (She was in love with him.)
2. *Toliko se zaljubljujemo u stvari koje ne možemo imati.* (We fall in love with things we can't have.)
3. *Kako je ona zaljubljena u njega!* (How she is in love with him!)
4. *Oni su bili zaljubljeni jedno u drugo.* (They were in love with each other.)
5. *Ona se zaljubljuje u maštu.* (She falls in love with imagination.)